About
About
Ever since I first got started with web development, I have enjoyed what I do. I have since worked for various companies, as well as freelanced on my own. I have learned many new skills, met many great people, and created many awesome things. I enjoy providing people with a product they are happy with. Now that I run Lead Web Designs, I enjoy it even more. I get to interact with people on a daily basis, providing them with solutions and making sure they are happy. It is our number one priority at Lead Web Designs. Connect with me and the team for any projects you may have in mind.

Our website is leadwebdesigns.com and you can e-mail me directly at rick@leadwebdesigns.com.
